{"tid":151752,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[經歷]依家D女騙徒真係幾厚顏無恥!!","createTime":"2017-03-11T07:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T15:47:12.000Z","uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba411145f10b277550099d159c22b764fa7c8404","tid":151752,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:04:55.000Z","msg":"話說大約4年前,係skout識過個女仔 <br />\n當時又係幾好傾 <br />\n個陣未有係高登留意美容雞金融雞D野 <br />\n結果好快約咗佢出來,咁就中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家諗返,都覺得個陣自己好撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上星期放假,去左某間位於商場既戲院睇戲 <br />\n買完飛仲有時間,所以決定係商場行陣先入場 <br />\n點知行行下,見到有個女仔幾熟口面 <br />\n諗諗下先醒起就係4年前呃9我個位女騙子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來係戲院門口噤電話準備入場 <br />\n突然有人走過來同我講野,就係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢同我講:你依家讀書定做野,可唔可以同你交換電話? <br />\n仲話咩想走出comfort zone,問我可唔可以交個新朋友?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當場reject左佢就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我心諗,依家D女騙子咁撚厚顏無恥既,以為過左咁耐冇人記得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇返條女FB,佢依家係大台巫婆琳死忠fans,諗下先發現佢自己同巫婆琳有幾分相似 <br />\n都唔知點解個陣會俾佢迷到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b098b0fdb4b7d74e6e211a603f54eb633c140f","tid":151752,"uid":81324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:07:03.000Z","msg":"呃左咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1999"},{"pid":"b7db940bae0c33cc98d09b9bdec36c28eb4ab05d","tid":151752,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:08:40.000Z","msg":"你之前中左咩伏先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69bad9006c5e8e0b5b85cbe4a35dbc073bd6fa5a","tid":151752,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:09:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你之前中左咩伏先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾人呃咗少少錢lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾多,唔想講"},{"pid":"4ae0aa74065fb804687a90cf1b8423595bd5a1d7","tid":151752,"uid":88829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:11:33.000Z","msg":"點中伏先 <br />\n不過 而家 好多 女做騙子"},{"pid":"1dab04c493644636b1b6543e1069053397a72962","tid":151752,"uid":1637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:16:32.000Z","msg":"你有冇中出過佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211308281b512c21642cb10b179a6629218fd2cf","tid":151752,"uid":48942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:18:43.000Z","msg":"開床單？"},{"pid":"01c313e5a7a5748fec0afe707c46df23c28ceb70","tid":151752,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:20:36.000Z","msg":"衰咸濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76270b7eb4d69d3a233a2d08ad76fccfcdede4c3","tid":151752,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:22:18.000Z","msg":"蠢就蠢啦"},{"pid":"78d4fbf9a138d416eb5ac8a94136cf4702befe82","tid":151752,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:22:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有冇中出過佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊有咁好命呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal